            <div class="badger-left" data-badger="Smooth Begin of Express Bus system">April 1998 - Beginning of Express Bus Operations</div>
            <div class="badger-left" data-badger="Smooth Begin of City Bus system">November 1999 - Beginning of City Bus Operations
        </div>
        <div class="badger-left" data-badger="Domination">January 2004 - Took Over by Sammi Corporation, Seoul, Korea
33 cities on 43 destinations with over 200 buses.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>